category: Graphics
requires: glib2 libSDL12 libSDL_Pango libSDL_image libSDL_mixer libSDL_ttf libcairo2 libfltk11 libintl8 libpaper1 libpng12 librsvg2
sdesc: "Drawing program for children"
ldesc: "Tux Paint is a free, award-winning drawing program for children 
ages 3 to 12 (for example, preschool and K-6 in the US, key stages 1 & 2 
in the UK). It combines an easy-to-use interface, fun sound effects, and 
an encouraging cartoon mascot who guides children as they use the 
program."
